Infosys Gains on Report It May Acquire Reuters Healthcare Unit

-- B y   S h i k h a r   B a l w a n i
-- 
2011-09-15T03:51:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/infosys-gains-on-report-it-may-acquire-reuters-healthcare-unit.html
Infosys Ltd. gained in Mumbai
trading after the Business Standard reported that the software
exporter is close to buying the health-care unit of Thomson
Reuters Corp. for about $700 million.  Infosys spokeswoman Sarah Gideon declined to comment on the
report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
